# UI/UX Redesign Plan - TDC HRM

## Goal Description
Overhaul the entire application's UI/UX to match "Modern Professional Corporate" standards, using the `ui-ux-pro-max` skill guidelines. The goal is to create a clean, trustworthy, and efficient interface suitable for an HR system.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> This redesign will modify global CSS variables and base component styles. Visual inconsistencies may occur briefly during the transition.

